profile_positions.description:
- Creating and executing a strong performance marketing strategy & execution plan for the team members;
 - Managing budgets and campaigns across all digital channels to drive strong return on investment and desired results with the team;
 - Ensuring successful planning, execution, optimization for KPIs via performance marketing campaigns;
 - Identifying and testing new channels to continue to meet or exceed established critical metrics;
 - Working closely with the management to share funnel conversion improvement ideas, feedback & present results.;
 - Develops and grows a team that fosters innovation and creativity;
 - Interacts & support clients to retain them in the business. In backend supporting the execution team members delivering the best results & client experience;
 - Builds the strategy and drives the execution of SEM & SMO campaigns and partnerships, including pricing, packaging, and positioning;

- Pitch Partnership opportunities to the Travel brands and Tourism Boards;
 - Digital Planning of all the associated brand partnerships;
 - Manage existing & new accounts as partnership manager for flawless execution
 - Generate potential leads for Partnerships through digital mediums;
 - Retain and grow revenue from partners;
 - Manage team to execute the campaigns of partners by coordinating with internal teams;

- Establish and execute a performance marketing strategy through multiple digital marketing channels including SMO, SMM, SEM, Email Marketing, Content Marketing, Affiliates/Associates and Retargeting to drive customer acquisition;
 - Planning & implementing campaigns to onboard new vendors and drive revenue from them via capturing their intent for subscription sales;
 - Strategy creation for Ad Sales projects & gettings leads for collaboration via inbound & Outbound;
 - Owning the Vendor Sales Team, providing  guaranteed business to them by maintaining healthy relationships with vendors.

- Devising strategies to drive online traffic to the company website;
 - Tracking conversion rates and making improvements to the website and campaigns;
  - Developing and managing digital marketing campaigns;
 - Managing partnership accounts along with their promotional strategies and activities;
 - Utilising a range of techniques including SEO, SEM, SMM and SMO;
 - Overseeing the social media strategy for the company;
 - Improving the usability, design, content and conversion of the company website;
 - Brainstorm new and creative growth strategies;
 - Mentoring recruits in the niche and company’s workflow;
 - Planning and budgetary control of all digital marketing campaigns;
 - Evaluating customer research, market conditions and competitor data;
 - Review new technologies and keep the company at the forefront of developments in digital marketing.

- Managing and helping create the marketing content to be used for social media outreach purposes (e.g. customer videos briefs, customer case studies, blog posts, posts from analysts and customers);
 - Building and nurturing social media platform-specific communities and audiences;
 - Support SEO strategies by understanding keyword priorities and how they integrate into content marketing tactics;
 - Researching  social media tools on a daily basis to enhance on clients’ social media strategy;
 - Monitoring and evaluating social media results on a daily basis in coordination with client’s goal and benchmarks;
 - Communicating to the team and management on project development, timelines and results;
 - Working closely with clients and other team members to meet the goals;
 - Keeping pace with social media and internet marketing industry trends and developments;
 - Collecting and analyzing data, related to social media marketing campaigns;
 - Assisting clients in identifying appropriate social media channels for their specific business needs and tailoring campaigns to the target audience;
 - Tracking performance of various social media initiatives and building strategy to improve business results;

- Aligning market opportunities and target account with strategic planning by making use of various online media such as Google Analytics, Facebook ads manager etc.;
 - Defining strategies and preparing proposals for social media marketing; 
 - Handling and reviewing of social media campaigns; 
 - Social Media Marketing (Campaign creation, audience analysis, performance management, reporting, projections);
 - Site / Landing Page analysis: Identifying, classifying, and designing the functionality and flow of information that comprise an effective user interface.
 - Build and execute digital media strategies across multiple channels;
 - Create, expand, and implement end to end marketing projects and campaigns, including ideation, creation and optimization;
 - Ideate and implement lead generation campaigns and strategies to drive ROI;
 - Monitor trends in digital Media tools, applications, channels, design and strategy;
